{"id":178688,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/global-voices-墨西哥：英雄报告记录善行/","date":"2011-09-12T04:00:42Z","modified":"2011-09-12T04:00:42Z","title":"Global Voices | 墨西哥：英雄报告记录善行","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://juarez.cronicasdeheroes.mx/reports/map\"><img title=\"Screen grab from the Juarez Heroreports map  \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Screen-shot-2011-09-03-at-15.53.25-375x216.png\" alt=\"Screen grab from the Juarez Heroreports map\" width=\"375\" height=\"216\" /></a></p>\n<p>华雷兹地区“英雄报告”截图 </p>\n</div>\n<p>“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://heroreports.org/\" href=\"http://heroreports.org/\">英雄报告</a>”为一非营利计划，借助群众力量，在地图上记录各种民众勇气与正面社会行为，源于<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://civic.mit.edu/\" href=\"http://civic.mit.edu/\">麻省理工学院公民媒体中心</a>的“Crónicas de Héroes”专案，由该校建筑及都市硕士兼都会设计研究员<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://civic.mit.edu/users/yesica\" href=\"http://civic.mit.edu/users/yesica\">Yesica Guerra</a>主持，针对墨西哥<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://juarez.cronicasdeheroes.mx/\" href=\"http://juarez.cronicasdeheroes.mx/\">华雷兹市</a>，当地因为贩毒暴力与<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Female_homicides_in_Ciudad_Ju%C3%A1rez\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Female_homicides_in_Ciudad_Ju%C3%A1rez\">女性凶杀案</a>频仍，犯罪率在全球<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/03/08/mexico-remembering-the-women-of-ciudad-juarez/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/03/08/mexico-remembering-the-women-of-ciudad-juarez/\">数一数二</a>。</p>\n<p>Yesica Guerra接受<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.knightfoundation.org/blogs/knightblog/2011/7/15/online-stories-courage-draw-juarez-residents-outdoors/\" href=\"http://www.knightfoundation.org/blogs/knightblog/2011/7/15/online-stories-courage-draw-juarez-residents-outdoors/\">奈特基金会</a>博客录影访谈片段：</p>\n</p>\n<p>以下影片是华雷兹地区“英雄报告”西班牙语简介：</p>\n</p>\n<p>“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://ijnet.org/\" href=\"http://ijnet.org/\">国际记者网络</a>”成员<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://ijnet.org/blog/director-crowdsourced-website-mexico-go-offline-build-participation\" href=\"http://ijnet.org/blog/director-crowdsourced-website-mexico-go-offline-build-participation\">Maite Fernandez</a>表示，这项专案构想源于2009年，“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://civic.mit.edu/\" href=\"http://civic.mit.edu/\">未来公民媒体中心</a>”主任<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.media.mit.edu/people/csik\" href=\"http://www.media.mit.edu/people/csik\">Christopher Csikszentmihályi</a>参与代表团，前往华雷兹市提供改善当地生活的构想。</p>\n<p>这项计划一推出便相当成功，在地图上记录共1045件公民善行，吸引墨西哥<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://mty.cronicasdeheroes.mx/\" href=\"http://mty.cronicasdeheroes.mx/\">蒙特雷市</a>起而效尤，该市位于<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tj-sd.cronicasdeheroes.mx/\" href=\"http://tj-sd.cronicasdeheroes.mx/\">墨国提华纳州与美国加州圣地牙哥</a>的边境上，甚至中亚国家<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.heroreports.kz/\" href=\"http://www.heroreports.kz/\">哈萨克</a>也有类似行动，虽然每个网站各有其设计及特性，不过各站隶属于同一专案，故目标与重点一致。</p>\n<p>“英雄报告”<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://civic.mit.edu/projects/c4fcm/hero-reports-cr%C3%B3nicas-de-h%C3%A9roes\" href=\"http://civic.mit.edu/projects/c4fcm/hero-reports-cr%C3%B3nicas-de-h%C3%A9roes\">期望</a>能宣传正面思维，以下范例是华雷兹市在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://juarez.cronicasdeheroes.mx/reports/view/1148\" href=\"http://juarez.cronicasdeheroes.mx/reports/view/1148\">2011年4月9日</a>的一则短讯：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>有天我从德州El Paso返家，在路上看到一名老妇下班回家，提着大包小包慢慢向前走，有位年轻人伸出援手，甚至用卡车载她一程。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>类似计划都试图用不同方式，在地方社区中运用数位媒体，其中好处很多，例如连结網絡活动与街头行动，使用情况与结果难以完全预测，有些通报内容已不完全像是事件记录，更像短篇文学故事。</p>\n<p>“英雄报告”网站让一般民众能够发声，彰显在深受暴力困扰的人口稠密区域里，仍有许多善行存在，也成为社会与政治比较记录里的有用素材。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/ernesto-priego/\" title=\"文章导读 Ernesto Priego\">Ernesto Priego</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/leonard/\" title=\"文章导读 Leonard\">Leonard</a> </span><br />\n · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/09/06/mexico-hero-reports-mapping-acts-of-kindness/\" title=\"阅读原文  [en]\">阅读原文  [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/09/12/9807/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%96%84%E8%A1%8C&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F12%2F9807%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F12%2F9807%2F&#038;desc=%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%96%84%E8%A1%8C\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F12%2F9807%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F12%2F9807%2F&#038;text=%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%96%84%E8%A1%8C&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F12%2F9807%2F&#038;title=%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%96%84%E8%A1%8C\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <